9 3. Property owners may voluntarily opt in to receive
10 assessment sheets, notices of change, and other official
11 communications by electronic means, including email or
12 secure electronic delivery.
13 4. Electronic notice and electronic record delivery
14 adopted under the provisions of this section shall have the
15 same legal effect as delivery by mail and shall satisfy all
16 statutory notice requirements.
